# Local env overrides — .env itself is auto-managed by Lovable Cloud and only
# holds publishable keys, so it stays tracked. Never commit these variants;
# they're where real secrets (service-role keys, third-party API keys) tend
# to land during local experiments.
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development.local
.env.production.local
.env.test.local
